result.title: CGI Animated Short Film: "Preheated" by Luke Snedecor & Sarah Heinz | CGMeetup
result.description:
CGI 3D Animated Short Film: Preheated Animated Short Film by Luke Snedecor & Sarah Heinz at at Chapman University. Featured on CGMeetup https://cgmeetup.com/project/preheated 

A boy's plan to bake a birthday cake becomes disastrous when his scientist father's latest experiment gets added to the mix.

Created by Luke Snedecor and Sarah Heinz at Chapman University
Follow Preheated on Facebook: facebook.com/PreheatedShort/
